title: Week 6 Studs & Duds + Breece Lightning, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/17
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, a review an upside down week of football! Andy, Mike, and Jason react to the biggest studs and duds of Week 6! Which players should fantasy managers hit the panic alarm on? Who will bounce back from a bad performance? Plus, lots of injury news, and the Week 6 edition of Monday Punday. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 17th, 2022.
